  <name>Ro-Start</name>
  <summary>Modern welcome application for Linux distributions</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="tr">Linux dağıtımları için modern karşılama uygulaması</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Ro-Start is a modern welcome application for Linux distributions built with 
      Rust and GTK4. It provides a fast, beautiful, and native GNOME experience 
      for new users.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Lightning-fast startup and performance with Rust</li>
      <li>Native GTK4 + libadwaita interface</li>
      <li>Real-time system information (CPU, RAM, Storage)</li>
      <li>Package manager integration (apt, dnf, pacman)</li>
      <li>Memory-safe and crash-free with compile-time guarantees</li>
      <li>Minimal resource usage (~45MB RAM)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
